Title: The Shawshank Redemption
Overview: Two imprisoned men bond over a number of years finding solace and eventual redemption through acts of common decency.

Title: Breaking Bad
Overview: A high school chemistry teacher turned methamphetamine producer partners with a former student to navigate the drug underworld.

Title: The Dark Knight
Overview: Batman faces the Joker which is a criminal mastermind causing chaos in Gotham City, in this epic action thriller.

Title: Game of Thrones
Overview: Noble families vie for control of the Iron Throne while an ancient enemy returns after being dormant for millennia.

Title: Inception
Overview: A thief who steals corporate secrets through dream-sharing technology is tasked with planting an idea in a target's mind.

Title: Stranger Things
Overview: A group of kids uncovers a series of extraordinary mysteries involving secret experiments and a supernatural entity in their town.

Title: The Godfather
Overview: The aging patriarch of a powerful crime family transfers control of his clandestine empire to his reluctant youngest son.

Title: The Sopranos
Overview: A New Jersey mob boss balances family life with running a criminal organization in this groundbreaking series.

Title: Pulp Fiction
Overview: The lives of two mob hitmen. A boxer. A gangster's wife and a pair of diner bandits intertwine in this darkly comedic crime tale.

Title: Friends
Overview: Follows the personal and professional lives of six friends living in New York City.
